PractitionerCountrySearchParameter

Parameter address-country:string

Searches based on the address-country field for the Practitioner record eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Practitioner?address-country={country}

ResourcePractitioner
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPractitioner
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
